headline: Is Archer-Daniels-Midland (ADM) Still Attractive After A 36.5% One-Year Share Price Jump
summary: Wondering whether Archer-Daniels-Midland shares still offer value after a strong run, or if most of the upside is already priced in. The stock trades at US$67.31, with a small 0.3% decline over the last week, a 17.1% gain over 30 days, 14.0% year to date, 36.5% over 1 year, 9.9% decline over 3 years, and 45.2% gain over 5 years.
